*
 * 不改变原始数组，倒序输出array
 * @param {array} arr 待遍历的数组
 * @param {function} handler (item, idx) => { // todo }
 * @return {array} reversed array default return []
 *
 * @usage
 *  reverseArr([1, 2, 3])
 *    => [3, 2, 1]
 *
 *  const origin = [{ x: 1 }, { x: 2 }, { x: 3 }];
 *  reverseArr(origin, ({ x }, idx) => x * idx)
 *    => [6, 2, 0]
 *
